This directory contains sources and resources to perform automated sanity testing of pictures.


WHAT IT DOES?
=============
It is the sanity test for pictures feature.
The description of test case: JPG file can be showned normally using Gallery2.

HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
mmm vendor/mediatek/proprietary/packages/autosanity/GalleryTest

HOW TO USE IT?
==============
1. Install GalleryTest.apk.
2. Push testimageJD.jpg to root directory of phone storage, and reboot.
2. Use adb command to run test:
adb shell am instrument -w com.mediatek.gallerytest/android.test.InstrumentationTestRunner

